---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="关于" description="关于天然未来派的摸鱼小屋。">
    <section class="about page">
        <div class="about__avatar reveal reveal--delay-1">屋</div>
        <h1 class="about__name reveal reveal--delay-2"><span class="site-name__segment">天然未来派</span><span class="site-name__segment">的摸鱼小屋</span></h1>
        <div class="about__role reveal reveal--delay-2">NOVELS · SHORTS · NOTES</div>
        <div class="about__bio reveal reveal--delay-3">
            <p>这里放我公开的长篇、短篇和笔记。</p>
            <p>内容放在公开仓库 <strong>belleangelina/writings</strong>，网站用 Astro 构建并发布到 GitHub Pages。</p>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
